{"title":"fix(remediation): increase mem-load container memory limit to prevent OOMKill","body":"Root cause: The mem-load container in Deployment/vigil-app has a memory limit of 32Mi but the stress command (--vm-bytes 50M) attempts to allocate 50MB, causing repeated OOMKills.

Evidence: stress: info: [1] dispatching hogs: 0 cpu, 0 io, 1 vm, 0 hdd

Fix: Increase mem-load container memory limit from 32Mi to 64Mi to accommodate the 50M allocation."}
